# This is app development ver 1.1 ------ by TIEN DOAN

This application offers a possibility to turn a Raspberry Pi as a sound 
device. the application come with 2 functions: a sound collector and a 
test tone generator.

List of content:
	1. Configuration Instructions
	  Requirement:
		1) Raspberry Pi
		2) Microphone
		3) USB power cable
		4) SD card
		5) Headphone
		6) Sound card
	2. Installation Instructions
		1) Upload all the files from this link to your Raspberry Pi: https://github.com/tiendoan99/app
		2) Connect your Raspberry Pi to the internet, sound card, microphone, headphone and to the power
		3) Set up your sound card using these following commands: sudo nano /etc/asound.conf
		
		
	3. Operating Instructions
	4. List of Files
	5. Copyright / Copyleft
	6. Contact Info.
